00:27:20.840 --> 00:27:23.660
And the ultimate experiment,
the best experiment

00:27:23.660 --> 00:27:25.910
that we've done so
far at mapping out

00:27:25.910 --> 00:27:28.940
this picture of the
infinite universe,

00:27:28.940 --> 00:27:33.560
