called The Microwave Anisotropy

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:37.550
Probe, that was the brainchild
of David Wilkinson, a Princeton

00:27:37.550 --> 00:27:39.999
professor.

00:27:39.999 --> 00:27:42.290
Well, he came up with this
idea when he was at Chicago.

00:27:42.290 --> 00:27:44.300
[LAUGHTER]

