00:52:17.090 --> 00:52:20.690
And so I'll just make a small,
little technical statement.

00:52:20.690 --> 00:52:22.250
One of the things
that you learned

00:52:22.250 --> 00:52:26.240
in Newton's theory of gravity
is that the strength of gravity

00:52:26.240 --> 00:52:29.240
that an object puts
off-- ugh, that

00:52:29.240 --> 00:52:32.330
