that the strength of gravity

00:52:32.330 --> 00:52:34.970
or the gravitational
force of an object

00:52:34.970 --> 00:52:37.250
depends only on its mass.

00:52:37.250 --> 00:52:40.850
In Einstein's theory, it also
depends upon its composition

00:52:40.850 --> 00:52:43.700
through the pressure.

00:52:43.700 --> 00:52:49.070
And so while we don't think
mass or energy can be negative,

00:52:49.070 --> 00:52:53.390
pressure can be
something that's elastic.

00:52:53.390 --> 00:52:56.060
If you have a hot gas,
that's positive pressure.

00:52:56.060 --> 00:52:58.880
If you have a rubber sheet,
that's negative pressure.

00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:00.464
And so P can be negative.

00:53:00.464 --> 00:53:02.630
And if you have something
that's very, very elastic,

00:53:02.630 --> 00:53:04.940
this combination
can be negative,

00:53:04.940 --> 00:53:07.700
and the gravity that produces
instead of being attractive

00:53:07.700 --> 00:53:09.050
is repulsive.

00:53:09.050 --> 00:53:10.220
Are you with me?

00:53:10.220 --> 00:53:10.720
[LAUGHTER]

00:53:10.720 --> 00:53:11.219
OK.

00:53:11.219 --> 00:53:12.470
I think you are.

00:53:12.470 --> 00:53:17.660
And so, stuff that has repulsive
gravity is called dark energy.

00:53:17.660 --> 00:53:20.325
So cosmic acceleration is
caused by the repulsive gravity

00:53:20.325 --> 00:53:20.950
of dark energy.

